    {"key": "ui.minigame.tea.tutorial.controls", "en": "HOLD DIRECTIONS TO HEAT. HOLD FOCUS TO STEEP. POUR TWICE.", "ja": "方向を長押しで加熱。集中を長押しで蒸らし、二杯注ぐ。"},
